For over two years we have had more than 100 players out there. We cannot claim to be an uber guild, nor can we claim that a GL never have made mistake or done anything wrong, but I can say that we have always tried as hard as we could to do right, and we have probably been harder than most guilds when it comes to deguild anyone that could not behave.<br>
<br>
To move players into the zone is easy to interpret as a threat.<br>
<br>
I do not blame any AD player to become upset about that, but I feel very sad about the public flaming. Send a tell, and you will find that a GL is very easy to deal with.<br>
<br>
See you in SF!<br>
<br>
Maybe we even will take him down together. Who knows?<br>
<br>
Goldi<br>
